ProtoResult:
. "Suppose that $m,n\in\mathbf{N}$ and $\gcd(m,n)=1$. Then the
   map $ \psi: (\Z/mn\Z{})^* arrow (\Z/m\Z{})^* \times 
   (\Z/n\Z{})^*. $ defined by $$ \psi(c) = (c mod m, c mod n) 
   $$ is a bijection."
